                 int iterations,
                 int inputLenght,
                 InputTypes sorting)
        *
        Parameters:
        heap - Object to benchmark
        iterations - Number of iterations the benchmark will run. The average running time calculation is based on the number of iterations.
        inputLenght - Lenght of randomised input data which will be used for testing.
        sorting - Is the input data random or in ascending or descending order.
